Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint
Description: y_{u,sp}=1 if User Story u is assigned to Sprint sp; 0 otherwise

Name: assign_task_to_sprint
Description: z_{k,sp}=1 if Task k is scheduled in Sprint sp; 0 otherwise

Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: a_{w,t}=1 if Worker w belongs to Team t; 0 otherwise

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: a_{t,p}=1 if Team t is assigned to Project p; 0 otherwise

Name: select_feature
Description: s_f=1 if Feature f is selected for implementation; 0 otherwise

Name: select_epic
Description: s_e=1 if Epic e is selected; 0 otherwise

Name: select_user_story
Description: s_u=1 if User Story u is selected; 0 otherwise

Name: mark_task_done
Description: d_k=1 if Task k is completed within its assigned Sprint; 0 otherwise

Name: resolve_blocker
Description: r_{bl}=1 if Blocker bl is resolved; 0 otherwise

Name: include_feature_in_release_plan
Description: r_{rp,f}=1 if Feature f is included in Release Plan rp; 0 otherwise

Name: achieve_sprint_goal_flag
Description: g_{sp}=1 if Sprint sp achieves its Sprint Goal; 0 otherwise

Name: sprint_workload_story_points
Description: w_{sp} planned workload (story points) in Sprint sp

Name: development_snapshot_created
Description: x_{sp}=1 if Sprint sp generates a Development Snapshot; 0 otherwise
